properties.otherAdvice:
Upcoming Bulga Bridge Closure need to be mindful as the Putty has had some recent fires and my effect response times.


The first closure will be in place from 6am on Monday 25 September to 5pm on Friday 29 September. During this closure we will be working between 6am and 5pm each day.

The bridge will reopen for the October long weekend.

 

The second closure will be in place from 6am on Tuesday 3 October to 5pm on Sunday 8 October. During this closure we will be working between 6am and 5pm each day.


Following the closures, maintenance work will continue to be carried out on Bulga Bridge until the second half of 2024, weather permitting. Our standard work hours are between 6am and 5pm on weekdays. On occasion work may be carried out between 8am and 1pm on Saturdays.
